For the acceleration phase:
\[ v_{\text{max}} = a \cdot t_1 \]
\[ t_1 = \frac{v_{\text{max}}}{a} = \frac{5 \text{ m/s}}{1 \text{ m/s}^2} = 5 \text{ seconds} \]

